OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe north and west remaining
OL,6,Fcloudy with a little light rain
OL,7,Fpossible. The south and east staying
OL,8,Fdry with some sunshine breaking
OL,9,Fthrough, becoming warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy in the northwest with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle
OL,13,Fpossible. The southeast will stay dry
OL,14,Fwith late evening sunny spells then
OL,15,Fclear spells overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother cloudy day in the
OL,18,Fnorthwest with light rain and drizzle
OL,19,Fpossible. Drier and mostly cloudy in
OL,20,Fthe southeast with some sunny spells
OL,21,Fbreaking through.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
